'use strict'
const colors = {
  txtMain: '#214559',
  txtMainRed: '#FE6165',
  txtDescription: '#757575',
  txtDark: '#214559',
  txtWhite: '#ffffff',

  bgMain: '#214559',
  bgMainDark: '#214559', // For screens > auth
  bgMainRed: '#FE6165',
  bgWhite: '#ffffff',
  bgError: '#fb642d',
  bgChat: '#f1f1f1',
  bgSuccess: '#25ce66',

  bdMain: '#214559',
  bdMainRed: '#FE6165',
  bdWhite: '#ffffff',
  bdLine: '#dddddd',
  bdInput: '#cbcbcb'
}

export default colors
